这个是我的emacs配置
1.把.emacs文件复制到～

~/.bashrc
alias evi='/usr/local/emacs-xx.x/bin/emacs -Q -nw'
alias emacs='/usr/local/emacs-xx.x/bin/emacs'

ubuntu install emacs
sudo apt-get install build-essential
sudo apt-get install libncurses5-dev libgtk2.0-dev libxpm-dev libgif-dev libtiff-dev librsvg2-dev libdbus-1-dev libgconf2-dev
sudo apt-get install clang exuberant-ctags
sudo apt-get install texinfo

note:
1.列模式
C-x r k 剪切一个矩形块
C-x r y 粘贴一个矩形块
C-x r o 插入一个矩形块
C-x r c 清除一个矩形块(使其变成空白)
C-x r t 在选定区域的所有列前插入样的字符